00:21:45.400 --> 00:21:49.480
And I heard, I think, Donna said
she speaks fast because people

00:21:49.480 --> 00:21:51.806
retain when you speak faster.

00:21:51.806 --> 00:21:52.930
And that's good news to me.

00:21:52.930 --> 00:21:56.140
I always assumed I spoke
